{"lemma":"جَهْرُ","slug":"جَهْرُ","root":"ج.ه.ر","root_slug":"ج-ه-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ه-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جَهْر","root":"جهر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":7},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":12},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6525","n6530","n6531"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%87%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to speak loudly"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be public, to be conspicuous, to become apparent"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to publish, to disclose, to make public, to reveal what was concealed; to cause attention to be brought to, to be showy or make a spectacle of, to publicize or public show of","examples":[{"text":"قُلِ ادْعُوا اللَّهَ أَوِ ادْعُوا الرَّحْمَٰنَ ۖ أَيًّا مَّا تَدْعُوا فَلَهُ الْأَسْمَاءُ الْحُسْنَىٰ ۚ وَلَا تَجْهَرْ بِصَلَاتِكَ وَلَا تُخَافِتْ بِهَا وَابْتَغِ بَيْنَ ذَٰلِكَ سَبِيلًا","english":"Say: Call on God or call on the all-Encompassing; whatever that you may call, the characteristics which are best belong to Him. And do not make a spectacle of you keeping close to God nor make a mystery of it, but cause yourselves to behoove from a course between that."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to publish, to disclose, to make public, to reveal what was concealed; to dazzle, to confuse the sight of, to surprise by an early attack and sudden loud voice"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to discover ocularly, to see without a veil, to regard without any veil intervening"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to deem numerous, to see in great number"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to admire for its number or size, to value highly, to honor"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to clean a well, to hit on water, to remove the mud from"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to estimate approximately, to guess at"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to shake the milk bag to make butter"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to travel over, to traverse"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَهَرَ (jahara) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of جَهَرَ (jahara)."},"ipa":["/d͡ʒa.ha.ra/","/d͡ʒahr/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6525","headword_ar":"جَهَرَ","root":"jhr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahorN","text_ar":"جَهْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jihaArN","text_ar":"جِهَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Er-Rághib, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing, A, Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, plain, apparent, conspicuous, open,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"public;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zahara","text_ar":"ظَهَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badaA","text_ar":"بَدَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealana","text_ar":"عَلَنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or the radical signification is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, exceedingly plain to be perceived,"},{"kind":"text","text":"either"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by the sense of sight"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by that of hearing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA.) [Accord. to some, when relating to what is visible, it is tropical; and when relating to what is audible, proper: but if so, it seems to be so much used in the former sense as to be, in that sense, conventionally regarded as proper. See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahorapN","text_ar":"جَهْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahura","text_ar":"جَهُرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", [inf. n., app.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahaArapN","text_ar":"جَهَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhuwrapN","text_ar":"جُهُورَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, great,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bulky,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) [and therefore"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a conspicuous object,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before the eyes of the beholder."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, pleasing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goodly, in aspect:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahaArapN","text_ar":"جَهَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below.] ―         -b2-  Also, (A, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahaArapN","text_ar":"جَهَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the voice)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rose"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to be plainly heard"},{"kind":"text","text":"];"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, high,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loud."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb, * K.) ―         -b3-  Also, (S,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahaArapN","text_ar":"جَهَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, high,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loud, of voice."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibir","text_ar":"جِبِر"},{"kind":"text","text":"aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaharN","text_ar":"جَهَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was unable to see in the sun."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, TA.) And in like manner said of the eye. (K.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaharahu","text_ar":"جَهَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahorN","text_ar":"جَهْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahara bihi","text_ar":"جَهَرَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A, Msb;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajhrhu","text_ar":"اجهرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Msb, TA,) [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi","text_ar":"بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajhr","text_ar":"اجهر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahowarahu","text_ar":"جَهْوَرَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made it plain, apparent, conspicuous, open,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"public."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahara AlkalaAma","text_ar":"جَهَرَ الكَلَامَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaharabihi","text_ar":"جَهَرَبِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajhrhu","text_ar":"اجهرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ijohaArN","text_ar":"اـِجْهَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi","text_ar":"بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajhr","text_ar":"اجهر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahowara","text_ar":"جَهْوَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahara biAlqawoli","text_ar":"جَهَرَ بِالقَوْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biduEaAy^ihi","text_ar":"بِدُعَايِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biSalaAtihi","text_ar":"بِصَلَاتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biqiraA='atihi","text_ar":"بِقِرَا=ءَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Sgh, Msb, TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahorN","text_ar":"جَهْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jihaArN","text_ar":"جِهَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bqr'A=th","text_ar":"بقرءا=ته"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajhr","text_ar":"اجهر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Sgh, Msb, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He uttered the speech,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the saying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his supplication,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his prayer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his recitation, with a plain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an open, voice; openly; publicly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahara bikalaAmihi","text_ar":"جَهَرَ بِكَلَامِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlqawoli","text_ar":"بِالقَوْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahowara","text_ar":"جَهْوَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biqiraA='atihi","text_ar":"بِقِرَا=ءَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he uttered his speech,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the saying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his recitation, with a raised,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loud, voice; aloud:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahara AlS~awota","text_ar":"جَهَرَ الصَّوْتَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he raised the voice"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to make it plainly heard"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahara biAlmaEaASiY","text_ar":"جَهَرَ بِالمَعَاصِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajhr","text_ar":"اجهر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jAhr","text_ar":"جاهر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made known the acts of disobedience"},{"kind":"text","text":"that he had committed,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by talking of them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"he who does so is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlmuEaASiY","text_ar":"بِالمُعَاصِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mujaAhirN","text_ar":"مُجَاهِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and simply"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mujaAhirN","text_ar":"مُجَاهِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA fiY Sadorihi","text_ar":"مَا فِى صَدْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajhr","text_ar":"اجهر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He revealed what was in his bosom."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHadiyva baEoda maA hayonamahu","text_ar":"الحَدِيثَ بَعْدَ مَا هَيْنَمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahowara","text_ar":"جَهْوَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He revealed the story after he had concealed it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajhr","text_ar":"اجهر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^amora","text_ar":"الاَمْرَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made the case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair, notorious."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaharahu","text_ar":"جَهَرَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He discovered it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ocularly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He saw him"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without any veil"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intervening;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajthrhu","text_ar":"اجتهرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he looked towards him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regarded him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA fiY AlHaY~i A^aHadN","text_ar":"مَا فِى الحَىِّ اَحَدٌ"},{"kind":"page_break","n":475},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tajoharahu EayoniY","text_ar":"تَجْهَرَهُ عَيْنِى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not in the tribe any one whom my eye regards as worthy of notice or respect"},{"kind":"text","text":"by reason of his greatness therein; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taA^oxu*uhu","text_ar":"تَاْخُذُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqawomu fulaAnFA","text_ar":"القَوْمُ فُلَانًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajthr","text_ar":"اجتهر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The people looked towards such a one without any veil intervening between them and him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He treated him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regarded him, with reverence, veneration, respect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"honour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or (TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he regarded him as great in his eyes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he saw him to be great in aspect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appearance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajthrhu","text_ar":"اجتهرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astjrhu","text_ar":"استجرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was pleased with his beauty, and his form,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appearance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state of apparel"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajthrhu","text_ar":"اجتهرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Lh, * K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he pleased him by his beauty and form"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appearance &c.:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it pleased him by its beauty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajthrhu","text_ar":"اجتهرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He saw it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(an army, S, A, K, and a people, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be numerous in his eyes;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajthrhu","text_ar":"اجتهرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S A, K.)       -A5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahara Albiy^ora","text_ar":"جَهَرَ البِيْرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahorN","text_ar":"جَهْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cleared out the well,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and took forth from it the black fetid mud that it contained;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjtrhA","text_ar":"اجترها","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or both signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he entirely,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nearly, exhausted the well of its water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or the former,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he reached the water of the well,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) in digging: or so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahara","text_ar":"جَهَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"alone: (TA:) and accord. to Akh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaharotu","text_ar":"جَهَرْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~akiy~apa","text_ar":"الرَّكِيَّةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I cleared out the mud that the water covered in the well, so that the water appeared and became clear."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) 'Áïsheh said, describing her father,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dufuna Alr~awaA='i","text_ar":"دُفُنَ الرَّوَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajthr","text_ar":"اجتهر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", lit.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cleared out the filled-up wells of abundant water so as to make the water well forth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"alluding to his rectifying affairs that had become disordered. (TA from a trad.)       -A6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaharonaAhumo","text_ar":"جَهَرْنَاهُمْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We came to them in the morning, at the time called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~abaAH","text_ar":"الصَّبَاح"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when they were inadvertent."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahara AlA^aroDa","text_ar":"جَهَرَ الاَرْضَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He traversed the land"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without knowledge."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.)       -A7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahara Als~iqaA='a","text_ar":"جَهَرَ السِّقَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He shook the milk-skin to make butter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and took forth its butter."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, TA.)       -A8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaharati Al$~amosu","text_ar":"جَهَرَتِ الشَّمْسُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmusaAfira","text_ar":"المُسَافِرَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sun dazzled the eye, and confused the sight, of the traveller;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asodarato Eayonahu","text_ar":"اَسْدَرَتْ عَيْنَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["A","Msb","K","TA","S","Sgh","Fr"]},{"entry_id":"n6530","headword_ar":"جُهْرٌ","root":"jhr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahaArapN","text_ar":"جَهَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in six places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n6531","headword_ar":"جَهِرٌ","root":"jhr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahiyrN","text_ar":"جَهِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}